{"tid":1228411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家搞到有人為你而死，林鄭你安落啦？","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:57:51.000Z","uid":232594,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b91f10d181658c85522e71cafdeb3c0c7eab3182","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"今日義士為抗惡法不惜犧牲自己，我係好心痛<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但呢種心痛我覺得大家已經唔陌生<br />\n早排係日日有人跳樓</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日上連登都會見到一單甚至幾單自殺<br />\n唔係學生就打工仔，個個壓力都大到爆炸<br />\n<br />\n垃圾教育制度令學生變晒考試機器<br />\n仲要有每日150新移民黎同自己掙學位<br />\n學生冇晒發展自己其他方面既時間同機會，日日擔心自己前途，呢啲你唔理<br />\n<br />\n冇最低工時，打工仔長期OT，冇晒陪屋企人時間，樓價貴到要用半個人生黎供樓，呢啲你唔理<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日100萬人上街反修例，你都可以視若無睹<br />\n<br />\n然後記者會就話，過去呢兩年都好平靜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>靜你老母呀 日日有人自殺緊呀</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n開口埋口就話出於憐憫要修例幫個<br />\n比人殺個女仔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>咁你幾時又憐憫下我地香港人日日好似死屍咁生存係呢個城市呀<br />\n<br />\n我地幾時先可以似番個人，而唔係返工返學返到隻狗咁呀</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽到真係嬲撚到我，好撚想嘔呀<br />\n<br />\n<strong>聽日大家一定要出黎，話比呢個假仁假義既柒婆知，我地唔單至要撤回修例，我地仲要佢落台，我地唔要你呢啲垃圾管治香港<br />\n<br />\n然後71我地要再出黎，話比中共知，我地要似番個人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要真普選</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c335d6f7bfaef73194b9041f10baed65739a96ed","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4868103a346890813a980a41449b32da164068f7","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4eef924825ce43e2d358966903aa39519a30704","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"879b78ab6e55b39724bc1eeb9f82c196cbd323a4","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a50be1f15057e486cabfe7802754856836d050a","tid":1228411,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65ae2dae780722f531ffc9750e9067fd77e62bc4","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:15:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb6f52830f14688cdb2863e4e436050f14644694","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d306e7be64bb686cac1050b4d3b41fd0e01a5efa","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1bd2277f7c939425d253e82a196f446d3fd7391","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3de1323b74deb104e21ffe5c173d3336fb5797c0","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:40:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18069404e9dd6855d7c5f27d278ffdc88f2117c4","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdc261c52b32c18657aa76d0ead8cd624487b8ed","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2caced3d73d2d0c738ff4f6d14d0356e428c33ba","tid":1228411,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}